title: Monfréville
text: Monfréville is a <a href="Communes%20of%20France">commune</a> in the <a href="Calvados%20%28department%29">Calvados</a> <a href="Departments%20of%20France">department</a> in the <a href="Normandy%20%28administrative%20region%29">Normandy</a> <a href="Regions%20of%20France">region</a> in northwestern <a href="France">France</a>.
